title: Charger Girl Ju-den Chan
resume: Fight Ippatsu! Jūden-chan!! is a manga series by Bow Ditama, which is also adapted into an anime television series of the same name that began airing on the liberal AT-X network in Japan from June 25, 2009. It features anthropomorphized characters representing aspects of charging electrical equipment. This series contains some explicit fanservice, including omorashi, which was broadcast uncensored. The series was also released on Crunchyroll, under the title of Charger Girl, Ju-den Chan, although it is censored.
